 natural carbonates by HR-ICP-MS</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Geochemistry, Geophysics, Geosystems</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/69d48d8823f0fcb6f2349350e6a74227"><gtr:id>69d48d8823f0fcb6f2349350e6a74227</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Misra S</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2014-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/91851B8F-16A4-4204-96C3-5475F31C0E6A"><gtr:id>91851B8F-16A4-4204-96C3-5475F31C0E6A</gtr:id><gtr:title>Pliocene-Pleistocene evolution of sea surface and intermediate water temperatures from the southwest Pacific.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Paleoceanography</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/bf4fc104d7c0509777776a5ff999566b"><gtr:id>bf4fc104d7c0509777776a5ff999566b</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>McClymont EL</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2016-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0883-8305</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/60E5F424-9804-4F17-BBE0-C9ADE28EE0B3"><gtr:id>60E5F424-9804-4F17-BBE0-C9ADE28EE0B3</gtr:id><gtr:title>On the identification of a Pliocene time slice for data-model comparison.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Philosophical transactions. Series A, Mathematical, physical, and engineering sciences</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/21f295d7bae68733041f7c3f2c605040"><gtr:id>21f295d7bae68733041f7c3f2c605040</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Haywood AM</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2013-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>1364-503X</gtr:issn></gtr:publication></gtr:publications><gtr:identifiers><gtr:identifier type="RCUK">NE/I027703/1</gtr:identifier></gtr:identifiers><gtr:healthCategories/><gtr:researchActivities/><gtr:researchSubjects/><gtr:researchTopics><gtr:researchTopic><gtr:id>D05BC2E0-0345-4A3F-8C3F-775BC42A0819</g